abstract_ssm: This collection includes the personal files of Jules Backman, nationally known economist and expert on prices, accumulated during his tenure on the faculties of the School of Commerce, College of Business and Public Administration, and Graduate School of Business Administration (now the Stern School of Business). The records include lecture notes, working files, syllabi, and correspondence.
